James. W. Warwick, Phys. Earth Planet. Interiors, 4 (North-Holland, 1911), p.229

"[The] dynamo theory has not yet successfully predicted any cosmical [magnetic] fields. Its use today rests on the assumption that no alternative theory corresponds more closely to observations."
alfredsnippet.name: Phys.org Post - The Solar Dynamo Theory's Failure to Predict
